Guud ahaan, marka fayras uu ku dhaco martida, waxaa marka hore aqoonsan nidaamka difaaca jirka ee martida ah ee loo yaqaan 'molecular pattern recognition receptors' (PRRs), oo ay ku jiraan 'lectin-type C receptors', 'toll-type receptors' (TLRs), 'nod-type receptors' (NLRs), iyo 'rig-I-type receptors' (RLRs).
Sida loo maro waddooyin kala duwan, fayraska wuxuu keenaa muujinta waxyeelada, bislaanshaha unugyada dendritic iyo sameynta interferons nooca I (IFN) kuwaas oo xaddidaya faafitaanka fayraska isla markaana dardargelinaya phagocytosis macrophage ee antigen-ka fayraska.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, borotiinka N ee SARS-CoV wuxuu u oggolaan karaa fayraska inuu ka baxsado jawaabaha difaaca jirka.
Wax yar kadib, jawaabta difaaca jirka ee la qabsashada ayaa ku biiray dagaalka ka dhanka ah fayraska.
T-nuugyada, gaar ahaan unugyada T-ka ee CD4+ iyo CD8+, waxay door muhiim ah ka ciyaaraan difaaca.
Unugyada T CD4+ waxay kiciyaan unugyada B ee soo saara unugyada difaaca ee fayraska, unugyada T CD8+ waxay si toos ah u baabi'iyaan unugyada cudurka qaba.
Unugyada T waxay caawiyaan in ay soo saaraan cytokines-ka caawiya caabuqa si ay u taageeraan unugyada difaaca.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, coronavirus wuxuu joojin karaa howlaha unugyada T isagoo kicinaya apoptosis.
