Bukaannada qaba calaamadaha neefsashada ee daran waa in la siiyaa oksijiin dhejis ah oo ka baxsan jirka (EMOC), oo ah farsamo la beddelay oo lagu daaweeyo wadnaha ama neefsashada oo daran.
Intaa waxaa dheer, ilaalinta dheelitirka korontada, ka hortagga iyo daaweynta caabuqyada labaad iyo shuqullada dhiig-karka, iyo ilaalinta howlaha xubnaha muhiimka ah ayaa sidoo kale muhiim u ah bukaannada qaba SARS-CoV-2.
Waxaa la ogaaday in falcelin xad dhaaf ah oo ka timaadda nidaamka difaaca jirka ay keento argagax cytokine ah bukaannada qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Shoogga cytokine waa qaab jawaab-celin caabuq oo nidaamsan oo lagu garto sii deynta tiro badan oo cytokines ah oo ay ka mid yihiin TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-kaasi waxay keenaan in unugyada difaaca jirka ay sii daayaan tiro badan oo ah xagjirnimada xorta ah, taas oo ah sababta ugu weyn ee keentay ARDS iyo cillad badan oo ku saabsan muruqyada.
Xakamaynta difaaca jirka ayaa muhiim u ah daaweynta naxdinta cytokine, gaar ahaan xaaladaha daran.
Daawooyinka loo yaqaan 'corticosteroids' iyo tocilizumab, oo ah unugyada monoclonal anti-IL6, ayaa loo isticmaalay in lagu daaweeyo naxdinta cytokine.
Daaweynta kale ee difaaca jirka ee la xidhiidha naxdinta cytokine waxaa ka mid ah xakamaynta jawaabta difaaca jirka ee unugyada T, xannibaadda IFN-γ, IL-1 iyo TNF, joojinta JAK, blinatumomab, joojinta calaamadeynta cytokine 4 iyo joojinta HDAC.
Steroids, oo ah daawooyinka difaaca jirka, ayaa si weyn loogu isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo halista dhaawaca caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, qaadashada qiyaasta sare ee steroids ma aysan saameyn faa'iido leh ku yeelan dhaawacyada sanbabada ee daran ee bukaannada qaba SARS iyo COVID-19.
