TCM waxaa lagu isticmaalay Shiinaha kumanaan sano si loo daaweeyo cuduro kala duwan.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, saameynteedu waxay ku tiirsan tahay isku darka qaybaha badan ee foomka kala duwan ee ku saleysan cudurka, oo ku saleysan aragtida TCM.
Inta badan waxyaabaha waxtarka leh wax yar ama waxba lama oga, sababtoo ah way adag tahay in la soo saaro oo la xaqiijiyo, ama in la ogaado isku-darka ugu fiican.
Waqtigan xaadirka ah, maadaama aan la helin daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay COVID-19, TCM waa mid ka mid ah daaweynta kale ee ugu muhiimsan ee bukaannada qaba calaamadaha fudud ama dhexdhexaad ah ama bukaanka ka soo kabashada cudurka daran.
Tusaale ahaan, shu Feng Jie Du iyo Lian Hua Qing Wen ayaa lagu ogaaday inay waxtar u leeyihiin daaweynta COVID-19.
