Bishii Febraayo 14, kooxda hawlgalka ee wadajirka ah ee ay hogaaminayso WHO ayaa loo hawlgeliyay Shiinaha si ay u dirto khabiiro caalami ah iyo WHO oo ku sugan Shiinaha si ay u taageeraan maaraynta qaranka iyo qiimeynta  halista iyo gudbinta cudurka  iyagoo qabanqaabinaya aqoon isweydaarsiyo iyo kulamo la leh hay'adaha waaweyn ee dalka iyo booqashooyin goobta si loo qiimeeyo  saameynta waxqabadka jawaabta ee gobollada iyo degmooyinka, oo ay ku jiraan magaalooyinka iyo miyiga . Bishii Febraayo 25, WHO waxay sheegtay in  adduunka ay tahay inuu sameeyo wax badan oo loogu talagalay diyaarinta cudurka faafa ee coronavirus , iyadoo tilmaamaysa in  inkasta oo ay tahay mid aad u dhakhso badan in laga hadlo cudurka faafa, haddana waddan kasta  waa inuu galaa marxaladda diyaarinta .
