Sanadka 2020, ma jiro tallaal ka hortaga SARS oo daaweyn ama ilaalinaya oo lagu muujiyey inuu yahay mid amaan ah oo wax ku ool ah aadanaha.
Sida lagu sheegay qoraallada cilmi baarista ee la daabacay 2005 iyo 2006, aqoonsashada iyo horumarinta tallaalada iyo daawooyinka cusub ee lagu daaweynayo SARS ayaa ah mid mudnaanta u leh dawladaha iyo hay'adaha caafimaadka ee adduunka. Ma jiro tallaal la xaqiijiyay oo looga hortago MERS.
Markii uu faafay MERS, waxaa la rumeysan yahay in cilmi baarista SARS ee hadda jirta ay noqon karto qaab lagu horumariyo tallaalada iyo daawooyinka ka hortagga cudurka MERS-CoV.
Bishii Maarso 2020, hal tallaal oo kaliya oo MERS ah (oo ku saleysan DNA) ayaa dhammaystiray tijaabooyinka bukaanka ee wajiga 1aad ee aadanaha, saddex kale ayaa socda; dhammaan tallaallada waxay ahaayeen kuwa fayraska qaada, laba oo ah kuwa adenoviral (ChAdOx1-MERS, BVRS-GamVac) iyo mid MVA (MVA-MERS-S).
Warbaahinta bulshada ayaa ku baahisay aragti shirqool ah oo ah in fayraska COVID-19 uu la ogyahay iyo in tallaal uu horey loo heli karo.
