Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, cilmi baarista ayaa diiradda saartay borotiinka S ee spicularka ah ee ka caawiya fayraska inuu ku dhex galo ACE2 receptor.
Istaraatiijiyadda saddexaad waa tallaalka ku saleysan nucleic acid (tallaalka DNA ama RNA, farsamo cusub oo lagu sameeyo tallaalka).
Tallaalada tijaabada ah ee ka soo baxa istaraatiijiyadahan oo dhan waxaa la filayaa in la tijaabiyo badbaadada iyo waxtarka. 16-kii Maarso 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka ayaa lagu bilaabay afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku sugan Seattle.
Tallaalku wuxuu ka kooban yahay koodh hidde ah oo aan waxyeello lahayn oo laga soo koobey fayraska keena cudurka. Waxqabadka ku tiirsan antibody-ka ayaa loo soo jeediyay inuu yahay caqabad suurtagal ah oo horumarinta tallaalka SARS-CoV-2 ah, laakiin waa mid muran badan.
Bishii Abriil 2020, in ka badan 300 oo tijaabooyin caafimaad oo firfircoon ayaa socda.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay daaweynta horey loo oggolaaday ee cudurka duumada, oo ay ku jiraan afar tijaabo oo ku saabsan lhydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Daawooyinka loo yaqaan 'antiviral drugs' ayaa ah inta badan cilmi baarista Shiinaha, iyadoo sagaal tijaabo oo heerka saddexaad ah oo lagu sameeyay Remdesivir ay ka socdaan dalal badan, warbixinnadooda ayaa la filayaa dhamaadka Abriil.
Falanqaynta horumarinta caafimaad ee tallaallada iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 ayaa sidoo kale la sameeyay bishii Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo fayraska ka hortaga ayaa lagu qiimeynayaa daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo lhydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo ay weheliso interferon beta.
Xogta hordhaca ah waxay soo jeedineysaa in Remdesivir ay waxtar u leedahay bisha Maarso 2020.
Hagaajinta caafimaadku waxay ka dhacday bukaannada la daweeyay remdesivir oo loo adeegsaday si naxariis leh.
Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee wajiga 3aad ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaali jiray daaweynta duumada, ayaa lagu baaray Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, iyadoo natiijooyin hordhac ah la helay.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, qaar ayaa dalbanaya in baaritaanka la sameeyo si madax banaan.
Mas'uuliyiinta caafimaadka ee Shiinaha iyo Kuuriya waxay kugula talinayaan isticmaalka chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee machadka fayrasyada ee Wuhan, inkastoo uu ku talinayo in qiyaasta maalinlaha ah ay tahay hal garaam, wuxuu sheegayaa in qiyaastaas labanlaab ay tahay mid aad khatar u ah oo dhimasho keeni karta.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine iyadoo la raacayo oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah ee ay ku go'aansadaan dhakhaatiirta daryeela bukaannada COVID-19. Daabacaadda 7aad ee tilmaamaha Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ku jira interferon, ribavirin ama lumifenovir ee COVID-19.
Macluumaadka hore waxay muujinayaan in qiyaaso badan oo ribavirin ah loo baahan yahay si loo xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide waxaa lagu taliyey in la sii wado daraasad in vivo ah kadib markii la muujiyey in ay xakameynayso SARS-CoV-2 heer hoose. Daraasadaha ayaa muujiyay in borotiinka asalka ah ee loo yaqaan 'spicular protein-activating serine transmembrane protease 2' (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka ACE-2 receptor.
Daraasadaha lagu sameeyay chloroquine iyo lhydroxychloroquine oo ay ku jirto ama aan lahayn azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaadyo waaweyn oo ka hortagay bulshada caafimaadka inay qaataan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasado dheeri ah. Loseltamivir ma joojinayo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana jirto wax door ah oo la ogyahay oo lagu daaweynayo COVID-19.
Naxdinta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa dhibaato ka dhalata marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyin ka hortagga shiqirka cytokine. Tocilizumab waxaa ku daray tilmaamaha daaweynta guddiga caafimaadka qaranka ee Shiinaha kadib markii la sameeyay daraasad yar.
Waxaa lagu tijaabiyaa heer qaran oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo ah wajiga 2aad ee Talyaaniga kadib markii natiijooyin wanaagsan ay ku heleen dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Marka la isku daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee serum ferritin si loo ogaado naxdinta cytokine, waa in la hortagaa isbeddeladaas oo loo maleynayo inay sabab u yihiin dhimashada dadka qaar ee la xiriira.
Daawada loo yaqaan 'interleukin-6 receptor antagonist' waxaa FDA-da u oggolaatay iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasado kiis oo dib loo eegay si loogu daaweeyo cudurka 'steroid-refractory cytokine re-release syndrome' oo ay sabab kale u tahay, daaweynta CAR T cells, sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda ma jirto caddayn la isku dayay oo la xakameeyay oo muujinaya in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CSF.
Wareejinta unugyada difaaca jirka ee la nadiifiyey oo ay soo saaraan nidaamyada difaaca jirka ee dadka ka bogsaday COVID-19 si ay u siiyaan dadka u baahan waa la baaray sidii hab aan tallaal ahayn oo lagu tallaalo.
Istaraatiijiyadan waxaa lagu tijaabiyay SARS natiijooyin yar oo aan la xaqiijin.
Xakamaynta fayraska waa habka la filayo ee daaweynta aan waxtar lahayn ee ka samaysan unugyada difaaca ee ay ku abuuri karto difaaca SARS-CoV-2.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, habab kale sida unugyada unugyada ee ku tiirsan unugyada difaaca unugyada iyo/ama phagocytosis ayaa suurtagal ah.
Noocyada kale ee daaweynta antibiyootikada ee aan waxtar lahayn, tusaale ahaan isticmaalka unugyada difaaca ee monoclonal-ka ah ee la sameeyay, ayaa la horumarinayaa.
Wax soo saarka serum-ka dadka ka bogsashada, oo ka kooban qaybta dareeraha ah ee dhiigga bukaannada bogsaday oo leh unugyada difaaca ee gaarka ah ee fayraska, ayaa la kordhin karaa si loo sii dhaqso u faafiyo.
Cudurada Coronavirus, oo ah koox cudurro isku xiran
Li Wenliang, oo ah dhakhtar ku sugan Isbitaalka Dhexe ee Wuhan, oo markii dambe qabtay COVID-19 oo u dhintay kadib markii uu soo jiitay dareenka faafitaanka fayraska.
